title: Anton Chichkan
text:
Anton Chichkan (; ; born 10 July 1995) is a <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>ian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er who plays for Russian club <a href="FC%20Ufa">Ufa</a>.
Club career.
On 17 January 2022, he signed a 2.5-year contract with <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> club <a href="FC%20Ufa">Ufa</a>.
Honours.
BATE Borisov
